snippet.title: BOH / trailer (2014)
snippet.description:
BOH is a dungeon crawler where you need to solve puzzles, collect items, open passages, avoid traps, kill the Evil Masters and the minions they generate endlessly, and ultimately come out of the mazes in one piece.
For detailed information, check out the website at https://www.retream.com/BOH.

WARNING: THIS VIDEO DOESN'T SHOW THE FEATURES/CHANGES BROUGHT BY THE MANY UPDATES RELEASED AFTER ITS CREATION.
